| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1895 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6bada1bf-fa3a-5418-8835-fa3f921d5ae3"
